enum CRC_BitSwap_t

Bit Swapping.

Enumeration which describes the supported bit swapping modes

Enumerator
CRC_BitSwap_MSB 

Most Significant Bit is first.

CRC_BitSwap_LSB 

Least Significant Bit is first.

enum CRC_ByteSwap_t

Byte Swapping.

Enumeration which describes the supported byte swapping modes

Enumerator
CRC_ByteSwap_DISABLED 

Byte swap is disabled.

CRC_ByteSwap_ENABLED 

Byte swap is enabled.

enum CRC_Operational_Mode_e

CRC Operational Mode.

Enumeration which describes the operational mode.

Enumerator
CRC_Operational_Mode_FULL_CPU 

CRC channel is operating in FULL CPU Mode. The CPU is responsible for the data pattern tranfers and signature verification.
